PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Rashed Abdulah UNDERWOOD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157154
COA: 339219 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 13, 2017 order of the Court of Appeals is considered and, it appearing to this Court that the case of People v. Ames (Docket No. 156077), --- Mich. ----, 911 N.W.2d 804 (2018) is pending on appeal before this Court and that the decision in that case may resolve an issue raised in the present application for leave to appeal, we ORDER that the application be held in ABEYANCE pending the decision in that case.
